{"tid":493813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清走家中「中國製造」物品 黃絲被除剩底褲：這是屈辱","createTime":"2017-12-09T02:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T08:03:01.000Z","uid":8129,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c01c8841f3ecbbb0e52637fad050b63adeb3bd7c","tid":493813,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"市面上不少生活用品都是「中國製造」，價錢便宜是一大賣點。日本有電視節目邀請一名男子測試，家中只要是「中國製造」的東西就直接搬走，結果令人大吃一驚，連男子亦被除剩內褲，引起網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n節目規定，該名民眾家中只要是「中國製造」的東西就直接搬走，不管是電器、家具或衣物，再經過一連串的檢查後，發現有多達619樣是「中國製造」，東南亞製品則有118樣，就連該名男子身上的衣服也脫到只剩內褲，讓他忍不住高呼「這是屈辱」。<br />\n<br />\n內地網民紛紛回應指，「質量好跟價格便宜就是我們的核心競爭力」、「所以我們要長途跋涉去日本買回我們中國造的東西嗎」、「你以為中國世界工廠白叫的嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%85%E8%B5%B0%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81-%E6%97%A5%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%A4%E5%89%A9%E5%BA%95%E8%A4%B2-%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%88%E8%BE%B1-025300007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0-%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2593%2581-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2589%25A9%25E5%25BA%2595%25E8%25A4%25B2-%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25B1%2588%25E8%25BE%25B1-025300007.html&d=%2BBnXBLBiaccT2F3aLLg4u54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fefeb705\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%85%E8%B5%B0%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81-%E6%97%A5%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%A4%E5%89%A9%E5%BA%95%E8%A4%B2-%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%88%E8%BE%B1-025300007.html</a>"},{"pid":"83831e07fb377c9b1aeff738b52e33e0e15215f1","tid":493813,"uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:57:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街啦五毛</span>"},{"pid":"021685d4a03500e949b125c177f407f1a2a0f99f","tid":493813,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":